<item>
            <title>[PIG-5315] pig.script is not set for scripts run via PigServer</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-5315</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ScriptState.get().setScript() is only called in Main and BoundScript and not in PigServer.registerScript&lt;/p&gt;</description>
